## Module selection (prefer over shell/command)

| Operation | Module |
|-----------|--------|
| Copy file | `ansible.builtin.copy` |
| Template | `ansible.builtin.template` |
| Create dir | `ansible.builtin.file` with `state: directory` |
| Install package (apt) | `ansible.builtin.apt` |
| Install package (any) | `ansible.builtin.package` |
| Manage service | `ansible.builtin.service` (via handler) |
| Edit line in file | `ansible.builtin.lineinfile` |
| Replace pattern | `ansible.builtin.replace` |
| Run arbitrary cmd | `ansible.builtin.command` with `creates:` or `changed_when:` |
| Run with shell features | `ansible.builtin.shell` with `changed_when:` |
| Sync dirs (rsync) | `ansible.posix.synchronize` |
| Set sysctl | `ansible.posix.sysctl` |
| Manage firewalld | `ansible.posix.firewalld` |

