## Pattern anchor files

| Pattern | Canonical file |
|---------|---------------|
| Playbook structure | `playbook.yml` (or `site.yml`) |
| Role task entry | `roles/<role>/tasks/main.yml` |
| Role defaults | `roles/<role>/defaults/main.yml` |
| Vars/vault split | `group_vars/<group>/vars.yml` + `group_vars/<group>/vault.yml` |
| Inventory | `inventory` (or `inventories/<env>/hosts`) |
| External deps | `requirements.yml` |

