## Debugging ladder

```bash
ansible all -m ping                          # 1. connectivity
ansible-inventory --host <hostname>          # 2. variable resolution
ansible-playbook --syntax-check playbook.yml # 3. YAML syntax
ansible-playbook --check --diff playbook.yml # 4. see what would change
ansible-playbook -vvv playbook.yml           # 5. SSH + module details (sweet spot)
```

Verbosity: `-v` task results · `-vv` + module args · `-vvv` + SSH (use this) · `-vvvv` plugin internals (very noisy)
